---
import { Font } from "astro:assets";
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';

import IMG_gardenBackground from '../images/garden-background.webp';
import IMG_sarahAndDaveLookingGlassSitting from '../images/sarahanddave_looking_glass_sitting.webp';
import IMG_sarahAndDaveLookingGlassStanding from '../images/sarahanddave_looking_glass_standing.webp';

const gardenBackground = `url("${IMG_gardenBackground.src}")`;

import RSVP from "../components/rsvp.astro"

---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<!--Not sure why all the provided favicon files are not linked here...-->
		<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/favicon/apple-touch-icon.png">
		<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon/favicon-32x32.png">
		<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicon/favicon-16x16.png">
		<link rel="manifest" href="/favicon/site.webmanifest">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<Font cssVariable="--font-header" />
		<Font cssVariable="--font-primary" />
		<title>Sarah and David's Wedding | July 11, 2026 @ 5 PM</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div id="main-header" >
			<div id="sarah-main-name">
				<h2>SARAH ELIZABETH</h2>
				<h2>PR&Eacute;OT COVINGTON</h2>
			</div>
			<h3>&</h3>
			<div id="david-main-name">
				<h2>DAVID JEFFREY ADAMS</h2>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div id="welcome-section">
			<h2>Saturday July 11th, 2026 @ 5PM</h2>
			<h3>Church of The Holy Communion</h3>
			<h4>218 Ashley Ave</h4>
			<h4>Charleston, SC 29403</h4>
			<hr/>
		</div>
		<div id="story-section">
			<h2 class="section-header">Our Story</h2>
			<p>
				It all started with a simple cup of coffee, 
				and somehow it evolved into a full-blown domestic ecosystem. Since that 
				first date, we’ve built a life filled with the things we love most: 
				Sarah tending to her garden, David dedicated to his writing practice, 
				and a home overflowing with books, music, and retro video games.
			</p>

			<Image class="center-image image-style-1" src={IMG_sarahAndDaveLookingGlassSitting} alt="Sarah and David sitting at Looking Glass Falls, North Carolina"/>

			<p>
				When we aren’t out for long walks, we’re 
				busy serving our four demanding roommates. First, there is 
				<strong>Marley</strong>, our Shih Tzu who lives by a grueling schedule 
				of "walk, nap, repeat" (with several union-mandated snack breaks in 
				between). He is joined by <strong>Eleanor</strong>, a Victorian Duchess 
				who is deeply confused as to why she was reborn as a quadruped, and 
				<strong>Teyla</strong>, the rambunctious kitten currently in charge of 
				daily chaos. Finally, there’s <strong>Donnie</strong>, the Russian 
				Tortoise. Donnie has a very demanding, high-profile career as a 
				classroom pet.
			</p>

			<p>
				Whether we’re digging in the dirt, hitting 
				a word count goal, or trying to stay on Marley’s strict walking 
				rotation, we’ve discovered that life is just better together. We are 
				so excited to step away from the garden and the desk for a few hours 
				to celebrate the start of our next chapter with all of you!
			</p>

			<p><strong>We can't wait to see you there!</strong></p>

			<Image class="center-image image-style-1" src={IMG_sarahAndDaveLookingGlassStanding} alt="Sarah and David standing at Looking Glass Falls, North Carolina"/>




			<hr/>
		</div>
		<div id="family-section">
			<h2 class="section-header">Our Family</h2>
			<p> 
				&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed 
				sagittis ex quis ligula ornare, vitae dignissim lacus elementum.
				Curabitur luctus est eros. Donec faucibus, elit nec sollicitudin
				sodales, est nunc suscipit nulla, sit amet egestas eros arcu 
				sit amet nisi. Phasellus at ligula eget ligula dictum tempus 
				ac vitae lectus. Nulla ultrices ante et est tempus hendrerit. 
				Integer ac odio at arcu luctus finibus. Nulla nec ipsum diam. 
				Cras viverra elit leo, sit amet tincidunt enim vehicula non. 
				In accumsan, sem bibendum finibus aliquam, nibh purus consequat 
				ipsum, et posuere sem tellus et eros. Sed id gravida nisl. Duis
				dapibus purus a semper efficitur. Nulla ut eros vel sapien 
				facilisis lacinia et vitae nisi. Mauris commodo, odio nec 
				porta laoreet, arcu lectus eleifend sapien, sodales aliquam ex 
				ipsum eu justo. Morbi ullamcorper porttitor nisl, eu cursus 
				urna tempus faucibus.
			</p>
			<hr/>
		</div>
		<div id="rsvp-section">
			<h2 class="section-header">RSVP</h2>
			<p>
				&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Please tell us if you will be attending below. If only some 
				members of your party will be coming, please let us know in the 
				notes.
			</p>
			<RSVP />
			<hr/>
		</div>

		<div id="lightbox">
			<img id="lightbox-img" src="" alt="" />
		</div>

	</body>
</html>

<style define:vars={{ gardenBackground }}>

	:root {
		--dark-blue-color: #0f1534;
		--light-blue-color: #345d87;
		--off-white-color: #ECECEC;
		--blue-green-color: #81c7a9;
		--brown-color: #625824;
	}

	html { 
	background: var(--gardenBackground) no-repeat center center fixed; 
	-webkit-background-size: cover;
	-moz-background-size: cover;
	-o-background-size: cover;
	background-size: cover;
	}

	body {
		height: 100%;
		margin: 0;
		max-width: 1000px; /* Or a width in % or ch */
		margin: 0 auto;    /* Centers the section */
		background-color: #ECECEC99;
	}

	p {
		padding: 0px 100px 0px 100px;
		font-family: var(--font-primary);
		font-size: 1.3rem;
	}

	/*In case I decide to use HRs*/
	hr {
		
		display: none;
		border-bottom: 2px solid #606060; /* Darker charcoal option */  
		width: 25%;
	}

	#main-header {
		align-items: center;
		background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #162048, var(--dark-blue-color));
		background-size: cover;
		background-position: center;
		color: white;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		font-family: var(--font-header);
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.25rem;
		height: 22rem;
		justify-content: center;
		border-bottom-left-radius: 50% 20%;
		border-bottom-right-radius: 50% 20%;
		border-bottom: 3px solid var(--blue-green-color);
	}

	#main-header h2 {
		font-size: 1.6rem;
		margin: 0;
	}

	#main-header h3 {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1.2rem;
		width: 65%;
		font-size: 2rem;
		margin: 0.4rem 0;
	}

	#main-header h3::before,
	#main-header h3::after {
		content: '';
		flex: 1;
		height: 1px;
		background: rgba(129, 199, 169, 0.5);
	}

	#sarah-main-name h2:first-of-type {
		margin-top: 40px;
	}

	#david-main-name h2 {
		margin-bottom: 40px;
	}

	#welcome-section {
		align-items: center;
		padding-top: 2rem;
		text-align: center;
		font-family: var(--font-primary);
	}

	#welcome-section h2 {
		font-family: var(--font-header);
		font-size: 1.8rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		letter-spacing: 0.1rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
	}

	#welcome-section h3 {
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: 0.05rem;
		color: var(--light-blue-color);
		margin: 0;
		margin-top: 20px;
	}

	#welcome-section h4 {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		margin: 0.2rem 0;
	}

	#story-section p:first-of-type::first-letter {
        float: left;
        font-family: var(--font-header);
        font-size: 6em;
        line-height: 0.72;
        padding-right: 12px;
        padding-top: 8px;
        color: var(--brown-color);
        font-weight: 400;
	}

	#family-section {
		display: none;
	}

	#rsvp-section {
		padding-bottom: 50px;
	}

	.center-image {
		display: block;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.image-style-1 {
		border-radius: 8px;
		border: 3px solid var(--light-blue-color);
		margin-top: 30px;
		margin-bottom: 30px;
		width: 700px;
		height: auto;
	}

	.section-header {
		text-align:left;
		font-family: var(--font-header);
		font-size: 38px;
		font-weight: 400;
		margin: 0px;
		margin-left: 100px;
		color: var(--light-blue-color);
	}

	#story-section .section-header {
		margin-top: 40px;
	}


	@media screen and (max-width: 1000px) {

		.section-header {
			margin-left: 80px;
		}
		.image-style-1 {
			width: 500px;
			height: auto;
		}

		body {
			max-width: 90%;
		}

	}


	#lightbox {
		display: none;
		position: fixed;
		inset: 0;
		background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.88);
		z-index: 1000;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		cursor: zoom-out;
	}

	#lightbox.open {
		display: flex;
	}

	#lightbox img {
		max-width: 90vw;
		max-height: 90vh;
		object-fit: contain;
		border-radius: 8px;
		border: 3px solid var(--light-blue-color);
		cursor: default;
		box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
	}

	.image-style-1 {
		cursor: zoom-in;
	}

	@media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
		h2, h3 {
			font-size: 1.3rem; 
			line-height: 1.4;
		}
		p {
			padding: 0px 40px 0px 40px;
		}

		.section-header {
			margin: 0px;
			text-align: center;
		}

		.image-style-1 {
			width: 400px;
			height: auto;
		}

		body {
			max-width: 95%;
		}

	}

</style>

<script>
  const lightbox = document.getElementById('lightbox') as HTMLElement;
  const lightboxImg = document.getElementById('lightbox-img') as HTMLImageElement;

  document.querySelectorAll<HTMLImageElement>('.image-style-1').forEach(img => {
    img.addEventListener('click', () => {
      lightboxImg.src = img.src;
      lightboxImg.alt = img.alt;
      lightbox.classList.add('open');
    });
  });

  lightbox.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
    if (e.target === lightbox) lightbox.classList.remove('open');
  });

  document.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
    if (e.key === 'Escape') lightbox.classList.remove('open');
  });
</script>